creator: Jonny Burger
descriptionHtml:
The essential app for all students of UZH and ETHZ! Join over 10‘000 users and benefit from these features:

TIMETABLE
All your lectures in one handy overview which gets automatically generated for you.

COURSE OVERVIEW
See immediately if you have passed your exam (UZH only). Also access information about your booked courses fast.

CANTEEN MENU PLANS
All canteens from UZH and ETH, plus nutrition and allergen info, as well as additional street food vendors nearby. You only want to see vegetarian meals, under 7 CHF, from canteens that are open now? We have powerful filters!

RATINGS AND GRADE STATISTICS
If you are not sure which courses to take, Bestande can help you. Our users have left over 18'000 ratings already and we have crowdsourced grade statistics that indicate how difficult a course is.

SEARCH
Find courses and rooms with our blazing fast search. Filter by semester, faculty/department, credits, and rating. UZH and ETHZ are quickly switchable in case you have a course at the other university or you need to find a friend.

RECOMMENDATIONS
We use artificial intelligence to give you precise recommendations about which courses you should take next. Together with our reviews and grade statistics database, Bestande helps you make great decisions!
Learn more on our website www.bestande.ch
descriptionShort: Your helper for UZH and ETH Zurich
